{"tid":2429123,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"楊明被控不小心駕駛等3項罪 今現身法院狂捽手指神情緊張","createTime":"2021-03-02T05:43:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-02T15:56:07.000Z","uid":212249,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"23a8a1d02d71d207dcbcdbe2b971c8207715bdb6","tid":2429123,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T05:43:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/dtz3sYEDszTJbCaEXitBC-Exwxs=/720x420/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/O2VK3RDAFNADBCAXYNMFDQMQOQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fdtz3sYEDszTJbCaEXitBC-Exwxs%3D%2F720x420%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FO2VK3RDAFNADBCAXYNMFDQMQOQ.jpg&h=6db07235&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今年39歲的撐警TVB藝人楊明，在去年8月7日深夜，於山頂馬己仙峽道自炒「石壆」，並撞毀一段有80年歷史的戰前石牆。事發後，滿身酒氣的他被控「拒絕提供血液樣本」、「不小心駕駛」和「車輛門窗玻璃附有膠貼及透光度不足」共三項控罪。楊明只承認兩項控罪，但否認拒絕提供血液樣本。案件今早在東區裁判法院續審。<br />\n<br />\n今早約9時，楊明乘坐女友莊思明專屬車牌白色七人車到達法院，並由兩位TVB經理人陪同。莊思明率先下車，見她刻意作斯文打扮戴上眼鏡，其後到楊明施施然落車，他西裝筆挺配以白波鞋，隨着女友步入法院。二人今次未如過往應傳媒要求停步拍照，神情顯得冷酷，追問楊明心情如何及對官司有沒有信心均充耳不聞，反而走到法院內才停步掃「安心出行」二維碼。<br />\n<br />\n未正式開審前，楊明坐在庭內，大律師清洪主動上前打招呼，楊明以手拍拍對方肩膊示好，之後便耷低頭睇手提電話，接着女友莊思明上前耳語幾句再坐回聽眾席，靜待開審，此時楊明神情略見緊張，開審後不時有捽手指小動作。審訊在下午1時許休庭，楊明和莊思明及兩位TVB經理人離開法院，登上莊思明白色七人車離開，二人繼續黑面對傳媒，下午2時半再開審。<br />\n<br />\n楊明入行以來負面新聞不絕，屢次挑戰法律，除了涉醉駕外，他投資食店去年亦被指觸犯牌照條例，早前再被爆位於荔枝角食店，涉嫌違例招待食客，分分鐘再惹官非。"},{"pid":"a38be0d2387ccc8d8682548f6e76047596a72b18","tid":2429123,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T05:43:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210302/YNHUFC6FKRFTZDSMW6J6FVFQG4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210302%2FYNHUFC6FKRFTZDSMW6J6FVFQG4%2F&d=a689Ea%2B9Xr9H89nGruQQA5tjV1Wc7Scp8ABb8MCffMw%3D&h=aaa9a574\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210302%2FYNHUFC6FKRFTZDSMW6J6FVFQG4%2F&h=09c74fa2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210302/YNHUFC6FKRFTZDSMW6J6FVFQG4/</a>"},{"pid":"9a2995bb872bd0824c8f95be12ceb163a0f3630c","tid":2429123,"uid":302347,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T05:49:02.000Z","msg":"驚閪咩，反正一定冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78c92aed210ad704cd22dcf3f06671446b0ddba4","tid":2429123,"uid":37874,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T05:53:57.000Z","msg":"一般人炒完醉到咁 仲要唔係第一二次<br />\n肯家坐硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過佢就肯定冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 愛國愛黨唔會有罪"},{"pid":"9885a4aaf7528269c846b525b738cd8793648ff8","tid":2429123,"uid":257272,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T05:57:03.000Z","msg":"驚閪咩, 唔好撞到D太出名既就得啦"},{"pid":"6c856a89468a543550bfb84be63355f6a867f450","tid":2429123,"uid":223741,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T05:58:21.000Z","msg":"扮咩緊張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fc78b40335dc4625c6b17fa4ee9da121a05cd06","tid":2429123,"uid":389053,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T05:58:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"85fe764449a401f191f0ef9773c29e7078a317b6","tid":2429123,"uid":19712,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T05:59:03.000Z","msg":"又幾好戲架喎 果然係演員"},{"pid":"19bbd1b686dd8130bc0cd4ea8ead2e92965c3047","tid":2429123,"uid":274722,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T05:59:11.000Z","msg":"楊明：我支持香港警察，你可以判我罪了<br />\n官：撐警高尚，無罪釋放"},{"pid":"a8c98a4c81f1f394a51163b9e30ce8cfcd7053be","tid":2429123,"uid":326712,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"1fc78b40335dc4625c6b17fa4ee9da121a05cd06","tid":2429123,"uid":389053,"like":0,"dislike":14,"sc